          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "C-12 target, thickness 20-, 45- and 95-mug/cm**2,",
                "were used."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SISD",
                "CSICR"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector telescope consisted of",
                "four separate elements, each (50*50)-mm**2 in active",
                "area. The first two elements-silicon resistive strip",
                "detectors(RSD). Each RSD was 500-mum thick and",
                "segmented into 16 independent 3-mm wide strips.",
                "The third elements was a 1000-mum thick silicon double-",
                "sided strip detector(DSSD) placed 148 mm from the",
                "target. This was segmented into 32 independent 3-mm",
                "wide strips with 16 horizontal strips and 16 vertical",
                "strips. The final element, 160 mm from the target, was",
                "an array of 64 CsI scintillators, each 20 mm in thick",
                "and with an area of (6*6)mm**2.",
                "The FWHM energy resolution was approx. 200 keV for the",
                "silicon detectors and approx. 1.5 for the CsI crystal."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "FACILITY": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "ACCEL"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                ""
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": {
                "facility": [
                  "PRJFS"
                ],
                "institute": "2FR GAN"
              },
              "free_text": [
                " C-10 beam was produced following the",
                "fragmentation of a 60 MeV/nuclon C-12 primary beam in",
                "a 3-mm thick Be production target. The secondary beam",
                "was purified to 98.6% C-10 using the LISE3 spectrometer",
                "and had an average intensity of 2.5*10E+4 particles",
                "per second."
              ]
            }
          ],
