          "COMMENT": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "*By authors*.Cross section for the production of",
                " Li-5(g.s-900 keV)=a+p in the M=3(app) channel.",
                " Although the calculations do describe the data it is",
                " recognized that the width of the Li-5(g.s) is not well",
                " known, there are possible a+p final state",
                " interactions. The cross section for this channel is",
                " therefore not unambiguously determined and hence is",
                " only given tentatively. A gate was applied across the",
                "  0 to 900 keV range to select the Li-5(g.s) events",
                "  resulting from the decay of Be-6."
              ]
            }
